A: You can use the following code to check if the database exists or not.
public boolean isDatabaseExist() {
    try {
        String myPath = DB_PATH + DB_NAME;
        File file = new File(myPath);
        return file.exists();
    } catch (Exception e) {
        e.printStackTrace();
        return false;
    }
}
